urce/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1385, \"end\": 1395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.652758159304521e-19, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Managing Director\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1204}, {\"ngram\": \"a proud supporter\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1246}, {\"ngram\": \"ParalympicsGB\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1275}, {\"ngram\": \"the study\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1302}, {\"ngram\": \"her excitement\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1328}, {\"ngram\": \"the upcoming summer sports season\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She commented: \\\"The Games always bring great moments to be remembered, and people remember where they were to witness them.\\\"\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1528, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Games\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"great moments\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1456}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also emphasised how beneficial the Games are in uniting people and offering an all-encompassing viewing experience: \\\"They are also a great opportunity to get people together and watch something where there is lots going on and something for everyone to enjoy.\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1793, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1574}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1596}, {\"ngram\": \"an all-encompassing viewing experience\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1648}, {\"ngram\": \"a great opportunity\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1684}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1698}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1727}, {\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1747}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1770}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This summer is a really exciting moment for sport and Paris 2024 is set to be a huge part of that.\\\"\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1848, \"end\": 1858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.652758159304521e-19, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This summer\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"a really exciting moment\", \"from\": 1809, \"to\": 1833}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1843}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge part\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The research revealed that 37% of those who tune into the iconic sporting event do so to root for Team GB, while 36% relish the variety of events on offer.\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 2052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1995, \"end\": 2002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9996486920892899, \"rank\": 0.00035142959794967426, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The research\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1909}, {\"ngram\": \"37%\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 1927}, {\"ngram\": \"the iconic sporting event\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1976}, {\"ngram\": \"36%\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2013}, {\"ngram\": \"the variety\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2042}, {\"ngram\": \"offer\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over a third (34%) enjoy witnessing all the countries compete, and an additional 34% appreciate viewing sports that typically do not receive much TV coverage.\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(34%\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2071}, {\"ngram\": \"all the countries\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2107}, {\"ngram\": \"an additional 34% appreciate viewing sports\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2164}, {\"ngram\": \"much TV coverage\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2211}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even those who do not consider themselves 'sporty' will be tuning in, as 29% still watch the Olympic Games when it's aired.\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2336, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Even those\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2223}, {\"ngram\": \"29%\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2289}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2319}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Specifically for TV viewers, a huge 83% will be soaking up the action from the comfort of their own homes, while others plan to gather at a friend or family member's house or at the local pub (both 17%).\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"TV viewers\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2365}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge 83%\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2377}, {\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2407}, {\"ngram\": \"the comfort\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2424}, {\"ngram\": \"their own homes\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2443}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2457}, {\"ngram\": \"a friend\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"family member's house\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2509}, {\"ngram\": \"the local pub\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2529}, {\"ngram\": \"both 17%\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Interestingly, one in five Olympic Games enthusiasts will only power up their TVs when Team GB are in action.\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2651, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2629, \"end\": 2636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9996486920892899, \"rank\": 0.00035142959794967426, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"five Olympic Games enthusiasts\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2594}, {\"ngram\": \"their TVs\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2623}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In light of this year's 'summer of sport', 33% predict they will be glued to the TV more than usual during the balmy months, averaging at twelve and a half hours each week - equivalent to watching eight football matches back-to-back, with an extra time session thrown in for good measure.\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2941, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"light\", \"from\": 2656, \"to\": 2661}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's '\", \"from\": 2665, \"to\": 2678}, {\"ngram\": \"summer\", \"from\": 2678, \"to\": 2684}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2693}, {\"ngram\": \"33%\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2699}, {\"ngram\": \"the TV\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2736}, {\"ngram\": \"the balmy months\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2776}, {\"ngram\": \"twelve and a half hours\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2814}, {\"ngram\": \"back\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 2885}, {\"ngram\": \"an extra time session\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 2913}, {\"ngram\": \"good measure\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite usually seeing a decrease in their energy use over the summer, 32% will be more conscious of their energy consumption due to the amount they will use tuning into Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 3124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3113, \"end\": 3123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.652758159304521e-19, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a decrease\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 2976}, {\"ngram\": \"their energy use\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 2996}, {\"ngram\": \"the summer\", \"from\": 3002, \"to\": 3012}, {\"ngram\": \"32%\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3017}, {\"ngram\": \"their energy consumption\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3068}, {\"ngram\": \"the amount\", \"from\": 3076, \"to\": 3086}]}, {\"sentence\": \"British Gas Energy, is rolling out itsPeakSaveinitative, offering half price electricity to customers on Sundays throughout the summer, including extended hours and two Saturdays aligned with major sporting events.\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3340, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3126, \"end\": 3137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Gas\", \"score\": 0.9993603799763404, \"rank\": 0.0006395956187487293, \"text\": \"British Gas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Gas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Gas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"half price electricity\", \"from\": 3192, \"to\": 3214}, {\"ngram\": \"customers\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3227}, {\"ngram\": \"Sundays\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3238}, {\"ngram\": \"the summer\", \"from\": 3250, \"to\": 3260}, {\"ngram\": \"extended hours\", \"from\": 3272, \"to\": 3286}, {\"ngram\": \"two Saturdays\", \"from\": 3291, \"to\": 3304}, {\"ngram\": \"major sporting events\", \"from\": 3318, \"to\": 3339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"O'Kelly explained, \\\"There is a lot of sport to be watched this summer and we are excited to be part of that through our partnership with Team GB and ParalympicsGB.\", \"from\": 3342, \"to\": 3505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3342, \"end\": 3349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/O'Kelly_Isley_Jr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999618012, \"rank\": 3.82744523713007e-11, \"text\": \"O'Kelly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/O'Kelly_Isley_Jr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/